div.small: The COVID-19 School Closure has left families concerned about obtaining a variety of resources. To assist families, Dawson-Boyd Schools will be offering breakfast and lunch. If you would like to participate in this service, please complete the following form. Upon State of Minnesota approval, these meals will be to no cost to the family. Please fill out this form as completely, timely, and as soon as possible. Delivery times to specified locations are between 11 AM and noon, M-F. Thank you.
